@node MAIN "multitext_plugin: Introduction"


    @{b}multitext_plugin@{ub}

        by @{b}Ali Graham@{ub} <agraham@hal9000.net.au>



    @{b}multitext_plugin@{ub} is a simple equivalent to the
    TEXT gadget in EasyGUI, that can also use a different
    font than the window is using. It also features the
    justification of the text within the gadget to the
    left, right or middle, and can display more than one
    line of text if desired.

